<h5>Advanced Inputs</h5>
<p>Optional configuration for customizing the scraping and summarization behavior:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Model:</strong> Gemini model to use (default: <code>gemini-2.5-flash</code>)</li>
    <li><strong>Token Limit:</strong> Max tokens per request (default: 50,000)</li>
    <li><strong>Crawl Depth:</strong> How many link levels to follow during scraping (default: 25)</li>
    <li><strong>Summary Prompt:</strong> Defines how each report is summarized by the model</li>
    <li><strong>Merge Prompt:</strong> Defines how multiple summaries are combined into a single report</li>
</ul>

<div class="d-flex justify-content-center pb-3">
