<p>After updating the desired inputs, click <strong>Search & Summarize</strong> to start the process. Progress indicators will appear on the page.</p>


<h5>Output Files</h5>
<p>After running a search and summarizing, FishTales generates the following file:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>scraped_sites.txt:</strong> A list of all the scraped sites to use to optimize the starter file</li>
    <li><strong>report_summary.txt:</strong> Generated immediately with summarized report data.</li>
</ul>

